With v6.5.0.14+ Single press switches relay. Double press switches USB power. If inversion is needed execute command `SetOption11 1`

Useful relevant commands:

`voltres 1`

`wattres 2`

`voltageset`

`currentset`

`powerset`

`setoption21 1`
